Summary: At low altitude, 500 or so feet. A house sized V shaped definitely NOT stealth bomber air craft overhead at very slow speed.
divs: Sighting DetailsIn edge of town, northen area of Salt Lake Valley, park like area, where lights are dim, I clearly saw the ship directly over head. Seeing clearly for 15 or so minutes. I was on a refreshing fresh air walk for evening. I planned to be out as long as I wanted walking in nice summer evening. I was glad to be seeing so clearly and up close an extraterrestial ship until I realized it could see me as clearly also. I felt very strongly it being a Grays ship and rushed home as quickly as I could because my fear of the Grays is huge.
